{"tid":1328964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請轉傳比自稱心痛被黑警打既遊行人士","createTime":"2019-07-18T05:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T06:02:41.000Z","uid":267639,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29b02db83471e5fbe71efb26ecf39f7cdb55f7bd","tid":1328964,"uid":267639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"721 真係好重要 反擊政府制造輿論<br />\n但最緊急既係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721 遊行 有70% 會死人</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>警察與市民既積怨</strong></span></strong><br />\n只有人夠多 拉走逗留人士一齊走<br />\n先有機會免於發生不幸事<br />\n再次呼籲遊行完唔好走 唔好散<br />\n保護逗留既人 (多數係青年)<br />\n繼承 &quot;要走一齊走既精神&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只要人夠多 黑警係唔會暴力清場 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>永遠逗留一班年青人<br />\n最後又話心痛<br />\n夠竟你地想點呀<br />\n要爭取定唔爭取呀<br />\n唔爭取既就一早唔好攪咁多野<br />\n要人地爭取 <span style=\"color: red;\">然後自己返屋企先</span><br />\n然後又講心痛D青年人比人打<br />\n係咩玩法</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔想比我地逗留 唔該成年/年長人士 遊行完夾走曬我地<br />\n一個都不能少<br />\nbe water my friend</span>"},{"pid":"a08000b7aea9ef49395847a9c00f4e70f1cea4d4","tid":1328964,"uid":267639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f99bc1a5d8526c8b33880955001f862add2e9d","tid":1328964,"uid":267639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568362c7fa363b1ded295ad4a0face704ee70ba5","tid":1328964,"uid":267639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fa04c38b106e743dcc3b8950747733b09b97ff","tid":1328964,"uid":267639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgm